Here is the Terraform configuration to set up a global video streaming infrastructure.

This configuration creates a private S3 bucket for storage, a CloudFront Distribution with Origin Access Control (OAC) to securely access the video content, a Route53 hosted zone for the domain, and the necessary SSL certificate and DNS records to tie it all together.

```hcl
# Provider Configuration
